 This install applies to "Global Gladiators" Â© 1993 Virgin - 2 disks.
 
 This install requires WHDLoad to be in the path. It can be found in the
 WHDLoad package.

 Game requires 0.5MB ChipRAM + 0.5MB any RAM (+ 1.8MB for Preload)

 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, NOVBRMOVE, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

 For the full WHDLoad package, other installs and updates refer to:
	http://www.whdload.de/
 or	aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
 and	aminet:game/patch/

HISTORY:

Version 1.5 (19-Mar-2021) done by JOTD:
- optional second/blue button for jump
- full joypad controls
- trainer infinite lives

Version 1.4 (03-Jan-2018) done by JOTD:
- (really) fixed level 6 interrupt lockup on checkered screen(issue #003402)
  (CD32 CIAs tend to emit level 6 interrupts that lockup the game)

Version 1.3 (17-Apr-2016) done by JOTD:
- added quitkey for 68000 machines

Version 1.2 (13-Apr-2016) done by JOTD:
- fixed level 6 interrupt lockup on checkered screen (CD32 & others).

Version 1.1 (29-Aug-2006) done by Bored Seal
- fast mem usage, bplcon0 access fixed, protection removed properly, slave updated for WHD10+.

Version 1.0 (16-Dec-1998) done by Bored Seal
- first release
- Disk protection removed
- BPLCON0 access fixed (4x)
- 24bit access fault fixed
- NI/MWB icon (created by JHZ)
- Quit option (your default key)
- source code included

Thanks to Chris Vella for disk image and Mr Larmer for his Cool Spot install ;)

joypad controls:

play: pause
rev+fwd: quit
rew+fwd+yellow: quit to wb
blue: jump (if option is set)

